        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[var(--color-text)] md:text-4xl">
          Solo developer. 15+ years shipping<br class="hidden sm:block" />software & solving problems.
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--color-text-muted)] md:text-base">
